s which can better predict the\nunknown directions of the solution. The proposed approach may provide some new\ninsights in the aspect of applying deep learning in Helmholtz equation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 27 Dec 2020 05:58:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-29"}
