 for personalized models on the edge devices,\ncompared to the state of the art.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 27 Dec 2020 09:39:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 31 Jan 2021 00:18:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-02"}
